        <body>
            <pb n="1R"/>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>N. Y.</placeName>
                <date>16 March/54</date>
            </p>
            <p>My dear Sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Enclosed the remainder of the Translation.<lb/> I am not quite
                certain if any portion I now send you<lb/> is already in yr possession—nor yet if in
                the first part<lb/> I used the <del>or</del> English “you,” or stick to the
                oriental<lb/> “thou” as I have done in this secd. Half.—I do not<lb/> care which it
                is, so that it seems<add>?</add> alike thro' the<lb/> whole translation—</p>
            <p>In yr place I would not displace any thing relating<lb/> to <persName>Judah
                    Touro</persName>, to make room for this Translation.<lb/> It will <hi
                    rend="underline">keep</hi> till next month. But <add>in any case</add> before
                you see<lb/> to press have the grandeness to let one see a proof.<lb/> I have in the
                former portion used “vision” for<lb/>
                <add>חזון</add>. Upon second thought I think “revelation” is better. Please
                substitute it.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I trust you will not fail us on <date>Thursday</date> next<lb/>
                    ply<add>?</add>. According to present appearances it will be the<lb/> crowning
                to do of the year.</p>
            <p rend="indent(4)">Yours very truly</p>
            <p rend="indent(5)">
                <persName role="author">Mr Raphale</persName>
            </p>
            <p>
                <addressee>Rev I. Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Ph.</p>
            <p>P.S. If you send me a proof I will<lb/> return it without fail the same day that<lb/>
                I receive it.</p>
            <pb n="1V"/>
            <p rend="indent(6)">
                <hi rend="underline">Paid<lb/></hi>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(5)">
                <addressee>Rev. I. Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(6)">
                <placeName>371 Walnut St.</placeName>
            </p>
